title: Daily League Of Legends content a long with other lets plays

embed.description: Sign in now to see your channels and recommendations!

body:
www.youtube.com/chookchookgaming

What's up friends? Chook here and I have a small Youtube channel which publishes daily League of Legends content along with lets plays of other popular games such as XCOM1+2, Dark Souls series, Fallout 4, Subnautica, No Man's Sky and many others.

I'm always looking for more nice people to join the Chicken Coop and play some norms with =)

I play with a few other small youtubers such as Myxthio https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCSnMLdsDQ8Gd9-QvDw8ETxg and Klixxed https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCMkuNbr0ixDerBGmg0Lw5wA who are nice and funny guys who deserve more subs and attention.

Hope to see you in the comments section and welcome to the Coop!

replies.body: Hey Chooky? You messed up the links to our channels by adding the ) at the end and it's part of the link. Mind fixing that?
